51
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:56,400
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, vjerojatno bih volio Matrix.

52
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:57,759
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, nema šanse.

53
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,000
[UNKNOWN] U redu.

54
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:58,319
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

55
00:02:58,879 --> 00:02:59,759
[SPEAKER_03] FSX Flight.

56
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:02,240
